data.title: Jesse Birdsall Height
data.meta_description: Jesse Birdsall height is 5ft 10  or 177.8 cm tall. Discover more Celebrity Heights and Vote on how tall you think any Celebrity is!
data.text:
DrJJ said on 20/Feb/11

Seen him too, some years back though near Covent Garden. In between El Dorado and Bugs, so possibly a bit down in the dumps and hunched. 5'9" absolute tops.

Scott said on 17/Aug/07

Incorrect. He lives in the same area as me in London and I see him very regularly in Sainsburys (I guess he's between jobs!) ... he's 5'9 exactly.

lappers84 said on 21/Apr/06

na i'm pretty sure he's about 5'9 or 5'10 no way is he 5'11, i was a big bugs fan he seemed about that height

Paul said on 5/Apr/06

Was in 'Eldorado', the Spanish Los Barcos style soap (1992-1993) that everyone used to either love or hate. Looked about 5'11-6'0.
